c: 17
v: 101
t: "Humne Moosa ko to nishaniyan ata ki thi jo sareeh taur par dikhayi de rahi thi (which were quite manifest). Ab yeh tum khud bani Israel se pooch lo ke jab woh saamne aayi to Firoun ne yahi kaha tha na ke “Aey Moosa, main samajhta hoon ke tu zaroor ek sehar-zada (bewitched) aadmi hai"